Author: shideneyu
Title: ğŸ”¥[PRE-ICO IS LIVE] ğŸ”¥ Liminality - Unstoppable AI that LIVE
Body: Dear Community,  As we prepared to launch our Pre-ICO, we discovered at the last minute that there was a double submission into our database due to an unexpected error. Even if there is no bad consequence, such error should not happen on a project of our scale, and we decided to relaunch all of our tests.  It has been a long week for the team, and we are not satisfied enough of what we have.  We could have launched the Fundraising and it would most certainly be fine. But we we feel like we were too fast, and as the quality of the code and the security of your investment are our Top Priority, we feel like we need to more time to proofcheck everything.  And as this long weekend is coming, along with the upcoming festivities, we just decided that postponing our Pre-ICO to the middle of next week, on December 26th, after Christmas celebrations, would be in the best interests of everyone.  We apology for that regrettable event and be assured that we take at Heart your support and consideration very seriously.  We will resume the Airdrop system starting from tomorrow.

Author: shideneyu
Title: ğŸ”¥[PRE-ICO IS LIVE] ğŸ”¥ Liminality - Unstoppable AI that LIVE
Body: Sure, do not worry. I will try to elaborate using simple words. Nowadays, AI are beginning to be everywhere. What we are trying to create is a new market, that we call 'Digital Friend'.  We want to create a virtual companion people will talk and get advices from, depleted on any dependancies or third party, which means that you will be able to trust it earnestly without being afraid that he subvertively tries to advertise products on Amazon, nor would he sell your private information to Meetic since you would have told him that you just broke off with your girlfriend. And that is in itself completely new.  We at Liminality believe that the day people will have Virtual Friends is near. And if people begin to trust them despite leaking their Private Data, it will be dramatic.   And to do that we are using IBM Watson to create a semi-deventralized network. It is helping us to create a first product fast - Majordome, a digital Conciergerie - ,on top of securing a contract with IBM as a client. And they will accept because with 500 000 dollars in budget we will be quite a big client. And we will negociate the contract for them to authorize us to put them in our front page, and allow us to name it partnership - because it is actually a Partnership. But shh, it's a secret    And finally we will completely decentralize it with our state of the art Neural Network after a while, to launch our second project, Numen.
